<!doctype html>
<html lang="en" class="scroll-smooth">

<head>
  <%- include('partials/meta') %>
  <title>AnimeLens - Privacy Policy</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Privacy Policy for AnimeLens Discord bot and website." />
  <meta name="robots" content="index,follow" />
  <meta name="og:title" content="AnimeLens - Privacy Policy" />
</head>

<body class="min-h-screen font-[Inter] bg-[#07060a] text-white flex flex-col selection:bg-purple-600/70 selection:text-white relative">
  <%- include('partials/gradients') %>
  <%- include('partials/header') %>

  <main class="relative z-10 flex-1 px-6 py-14">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight bg-gradient-to-br from-white via-purple-100 to-purple-300 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/70">Last updated: <%= new Date().toISOString().slice(0,10) %></p>

      <div class="mt-8 space-y-8 text-sm leading-7 text-white/80">
        <section class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Overview</h2>
          <p>
            AnimeLens (the "Bot" and the "Website") values your privacy. This policy explains what limited information we process and how we handle it when you use the Bot in Discord or visit this Website.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Data We Process</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li><span class="font-medium">Discord identifiers:</span> guild IDs, channel IDs, and user IDs only as needed to operate commands and features.</li>
            <li><span class="font-medium">Command usage metadata:</span> basic command stats (e.g., counts, timestamps) to improve reliability and prevent abuse.</li>
            <li><span class="font-medium">OAuth tokens for integrations:</span> if you link third‑party services (e.g., MyAnimeList), we store only the tokens required to keep your account linked. You can unlink at any time.</li>
            <li><span class="font-medium">Transient logs:</span> short‑lived logs for debugging and uptime monitoring.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">How We Use Information</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>To provide Bot functionality, respond to commands, and integrate with supported services.</li>
            <li>To monitor uptime, performance, abuse, and ensure fair usage (e.g., cooldowns and rate limiting).</li>
            <li>To improve features and overall quality of the Bot.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Retention</h2>
          <p>
            Identifiers and tokens are retained only while needed to provide the features you enabled. Transient logs are short‑lived. You can request deletion of stored data associated with your user ID at any time.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Security</h2>
          <p>
            We apply reasonable technical and organizational measures to safeguard stored tokens and identifiers. However, no method of transmission or storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Third‑Party Services</h2>
          <p>
            The Bot may interact with third‑party services (e.g., MyAnimeList APIs or bot listing sites you vote on). Your use of those services is governed by their respective policies and terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Your Choices</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2">
            <li>Unlink integrations at any time to revoke access tokens.</li>
            <li>Request deletion of stored data tied to your Discord user ID.</li>
            <li>Remove the Bot from your server to stop further processing there.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/5 p-5">
          <h2 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For privacy requests or questions, please reach out via Discord to the developer (<a href="https://discord.com/users/" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white">@nonlooped</a>) or via the contact links on <a href="https://thelooped.tech/" class="underline decoration-white/30 hover:decoration-white" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">thelooped.tech</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include('partials/footer') %>
</body>

</html>
